revision.text: ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Yellowhairs}} # {{surname|en|from=Navajo}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yellowhair'' is the 30735<sup>th</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 758 individuals. ''Yellowhair'' is most common among American Indian/Alaska Native (94.46%) individuals.
